2 law enforcement agency, or local law enforcement agency to search the
3 premises of the licensee's hemp operation.
4 (g) If the state police department, a federal law enforcement agency,
5 or a local law enforcement agency cooperates with the state seed
6 commissioner in the detention, seizure, or embargo of a crop under this
